Package: rnrfa
Type: Package
Version: 0.2.0
Title: UK National River Flow Archive data from R
Description: Utility functions to retrieve data from the UK National River Flow
    Archive. The package contains R wrappers to the UK NRFA data temporary-API
    (http://www.ceh.ac.uk/data/nrfa/). There are functions to retrieve stations
    falling in a bounding box, to generate a map and extracting time series and
    general information. It also contain the dataset 'StationSummary'.
